text: decent experience. the staff working there was good. wanted to see more of Wyn Lyn's work but the gallery was small and space was given to other notable artists.

The best contemporary art gallery in Singapore with an exciting stable of local artists across several mediums (installations, paintings, photography etc). Works are generally of a high standard and it's great to see a gallery supporting Singaporean talent across different career progressions.
Love the artworks on display in this gallery.
